workshop.controllers.internal.rest

Interface WorkshopRestController<T extends WorkshopEntity>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Every implementation must be typed with WorkshopEntity of internal domain.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AuthorityPermissionsRestController, ClassifierGroupsRestController, ClassifiersRestController, DepartmentsRestController, EmployeesRestController, ExternalAuthoritiesRestController, InternalAuthoritiesRestController, OrdersRestController, PhonesRestController, PositionsRestController, TasksRestController, UsersRestController, WorkshopEntityTypesRestController, WorkshopRestControllerAbstract

    public interface WorkshopRestController<T extends WorkshopEntity>
    Spring specified controllers contract. To be inherited by all the REST Controllers to work with WorkshopEntities.
